verbose_text: Rabconnectin-3 alpha and beta (Rbcn-3A and B) regulate the V-ATPase proton pump and mutations in Rbcn-3A and Rbcn-3B cause defects in endocytic trafficking and the accumulation of Notch in late endosomal compartments in Drosophila XREF_BIBR.
evidence: Rbcn-3A and Rbcn-3B cause defects in endocytic trafficking and the accumulation of Notch
